0\r\nRelease: 0.0.24039.713.20151013gite09159a.el6\r\n\r\nWith the default setting:\r\n{code}\r\n# euctl | grep cloud.vmtypes.format_ephemeral_storage\r\ncloud.vmtypes.format_ephemeral_storage = true\r\n\r\n# euca-describe-images emi-478b26ca\r\nIMAGE\temi-478b26ca\teutester-installed/precise-server-cloudimg-amd64-disk1.img.manifest.xml\t000302882846\tavailable\tpublic\tx86_64\tmachine\t\t\t\tinstance-store\thvm\r\n\r\n$ sudo parted /dev/vdb\r\nGNU Parted 2.3\r\nUsing /dev/vdb\r\nWelcome to GNU Parted! Type 'help' to view a list of commands.\r\n(parted) p                                                                \r\nModel: Virtio Block Device (virtblk)\r\nDisk /dev/vdb: 3221MB\r\nSector size (logical/physical): 512B/512B\r\nPartition Table: loop\r\n\r\nNumber  Start  End     Size    File system  Flags\r\n 1      0.00B  3221MB  3221MB  ext3\r\n{code}\r\nChanged to false and launched a new instance from the same EMI:\r\n{code}\r\n# euctl cloud.vmtypes.format_ephemeral_storage=false\r\ncloud.vmtypes.format_ephemeral_storage = false\r\n\r\n$ sudo parted /dev/vdb\r\nGNU Parted 2.3\r\nUsing /dev/vdb\r\nWelcome to GNU Parted! Type 'help' to view a list of commands.\r\n(parted) p                                                                \r\nError: /dev/vdb: unrecognised disk label \r\n{code}","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=rusvika","name":"rusvika","key":"rusvika","accountId":"557058:0f138bdf-f1d0-4468-9edd-e45575af47da","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c975ce5391bf03e1a9aa2a957435569b?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Drusvika%26avatarId%3D10701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c975ce5391bf03e1a9aa2a957435569b?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Drusvika%26avatarId%3D10701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c975ce5391bf03e1a9aa2a957